OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy at first as bands of
OL,6,Frain push northeast. Showers follow
OL,7,Ffrom the west, some heavy and
OL,8,Fthundery. Chance of a few brighter
OL,9,Fbreaks in shelter.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FShowers or longer spells of
OL,12,Frain spread in through the evening and
OL,13,Fovernight, the rain heavy and thundery
OL,14,Fat times. Windy around the coasts.
OL,15,
OL,16,CThursday:FShowers occasionally forming
OL,17,Flonger spells of rain, heavy and
OL,18,Fthundery at times. Becoming drier
OL,19,Flater through the day. Windy at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
