OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FA band
OL,6,Fof rain pushes east Friday with
OL,7,Fshowers following later. Showers or
OL,8,Flonger spells of rain on Saturday.
OL,9,FOccasionally windy. Mostly dry, bright
OL,10,FSunday, chance of the odd shower.
